<plot>Gordion hires a young man names Steve to prepare a set of 6 Tarot Cards out of human skin for a ritual he is about to perform. When Gordion performs some duties back for Steve in exchange for his services, Gordion proceeds with the rituals which involves sewing the Tarot Cards into his own skin. Gordion dies during the process and is sent to Purgatory where The Keeper looks back at his life to decide whether he would go to heaven or hell, or be a pal!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?103242</url></doc>
